<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Exclude on cmdragon's Blog</title><link>https://blog.cmdragon.cn/tags/exclude/</link><description>Recent content in Exclude on cmdragon's Blog</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 14:30:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.cmdragon.cn/tags/exclude/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>不是所有组件都值得缓存——include和exclude怎么挑</title><link>https://blog.cmdragon.cn/posts/k2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1e2f3a4b5c6d7/</link><pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 14:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.cmdragon.cn/posts/k2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1e2f3a4b5c6d7/</guid><description>KeepAlive默认会把所有子组件都缓存，但有些组件缓存了反而占内存。include和exclude让你精准控制谁该缓存谁不该缓存，支持字符串、正则、数组三种写法，关键是组件的name要对得上。</description></item></channel></rss>